                        <div id="page-title">
                            Site-CN-65代主管助理Dr. Hazard的人事档案
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        




<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">你打开了Dr.&nbsp;Hazard落在办公室里的随身听。</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">你关掉了随声听。</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="433" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=1334780738&auto=0&height=66"></iframe></p>
<p><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="433" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=1334778977&auto=0&height=66"></iframe></p>
<p><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="433" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=1334778975&auto=0&height=66"></iframe></p>
<p><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="433" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=32431729&auto=0&height=66"></iframe></p>
<p><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="433" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=423118341&auto=0&height=66"></iframe></p>
<p><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="433" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=32432413&auto=0&height=66"></iframe></p>
<p><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="433" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=26319684&auto=1&height=66"></iframe></p>
